description:
Oh yepp. 
I absolutely do look like a f*cking scary ""conspiracy theorist"" - so please, attention! Haha.
. 
But neither, I would say I am one of those called a Hippie-Soul.
I'd love to be free as the wind, and okay, maybe I don't like following rules.
But I'm open minded and try to be nonjudgemental.
I just enjoy the journey of my life and want to see me,
and YOU - I want us to grow.
I'm neither a leader nor a follower -
and for me, that's the point.
I do own my own blissful path.
I believe, that people should love more and hate less.
And I feel it in my bones, that it's more than the right, to stand up and use my voice for the True. 
It's really that simple.
✨
It's a
#loverevolution.
I'm a #truther ❤️ Totally dangerous, yepp.
